channel.title: Interception 742 Source Mirror
channel.description:
[center]Hello im releasing a source that ive been working on for a few weeks. I am ~Tehpk~/Thatpsycho. Idc if you flame im just here to release a server. features and pictures below.
Features: Prestiging - 10 prestige levels no shop yet. Loyalty System w/shop Wings all work Squeal of Fortune 99% Money Pouch clue Scrolls File Implemented but not finished Grotworms Dungeon Polypore Dungeon Level Points with shop The ability to click a skill and either open a shop or teleport to the training location. Clan Wars all portals 100% Character Design Troll Invasion minigame Zombies Minigame Working Runespan - glitchy all skill trainable Player Owned Homes - with the ability to make objects, they dont show up but you can train construction by continuously remaking stuff Sawmill operator 100% all working curses Completionists cape stand working Torva/Pernix/Virtus degrade and can be repaired Quest system added Commands file tweaked/fixed ::sellall command Over 1500 NPCs Spawned all skill interfaces fixed Teleport Crystal Working Hunter Pking is near perfected Donator zone Extreme Donator Zone Halfway done Lots more cant remember it all.... + all matrix features Pk/skill ECO Shops perfected Lucky Items and their special attacks/stats
Npc's
King Black Dragon (737 one) Queen Black Dragon Tormented Demons with all prayers and attacks Nex Full Godwars Dungeon, with teleports and working altars ( with timers ) Corporeal beast Frost dragons Dominion Tower Glacors Nomads Requim Bork The Inadequancy The Illusive Kalphite Queen All stages and attacks + more.

item.dc:creator: @Roos-Skywalker Roos-Skywalker
item.description:
@Roos-Skywalker wrote:

First of all, I would like to thank you for your amazing resource ‘‘Interception 742’’.
Unfortunately, I have experienced an issue with running. When I ran the program I received an error indicating that it could not load Cache in the Data folder. Therefore I created a Cache folder in the Data folder but since I am not a programmer, I have absolutely no clue what to do next! http://imgur.com/ypqEBcD
I have absolutely no idea what this means.
http://imgur.com/y7ybMR2
My best guess is that it is missing files that should be in that folder but aren’t there.
Please pardon me for my n00bness, playing around with routers is more my thing.

Here are my specs so you can help me better.
I am using a 64bits Windows 7 and JDK. I use 32bits and 64bits JRE respectively, however since all the paths go to C:/Program Files 32bits Java is left unused.
I have replaced al Java 7 paths with Java 8 paths. For example: This is what the compiler looks like:
[spoiler]@echo off
echo Compiling…
“C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.8.0_45/bin/javac.exe” -d bin -cp lib/; -sourcepath src src/com/rs/.java
@echo Finished.
pause[/spoiler]
[size=8pt]The reason why my Windows looks like shit is because I prioritize performance over looks.[/size]
If anyone can help me I would be extremely grateful.
